Amtrak.data <- read.csv("data-raw/Amtrak data.csv")
Amtrak.data
ridership.ts <- ts(Amtrak.data$Ridership, start = c(1991, 1), end = c(2004, 3), freq = 12)
plot(ridership.ts, xlab = "Time", ylab = "Ridership", ylim = c(1300, 2300), bty = "l")
